com.facebook.react.uimanager

Interface BaseViewManagerInterface<T extends android.view.View>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ARTSurfaceViewManager, BaseViewManager, BaseViewManagerAdapter, ReactCheckBoxManager, ReactClippingViewManager, ReactDialogPickerManager, ReactDrawerLayoutManager, ReactDropdownPickerManager, ReactHorizontalScrollContainerViewManager, ReactHorizontalScrollViewManager, ReactImageManager, ReactModalHostManager, ReactPickerManager, ReactProgressBarViewManager, ReactScrollViewManager, ReactSliderManager, ReactSwitchManager, ReactTextAnchorViewManager, ReactTextInputManager, ReactTextViewManager, ReactUnimplementedViewManager, ReactViewManager, ReactViewPagerManager, ReactVirtualTextViewManager, RootViewManager, SimpleViewManager, SwipeRefreshLayoutManager, ViewGroupManager

    public interface BaseViewManagerInterface<T extends android.view.View>
    This is an interface that should be implemented by view managers supporting the base view properties such as backgroundColor, opacity, etc.
